        <Parent_String>architecture (discipline) [300054156], visual arts (discipline) [300054154], arts (broad discipline) [300175240], arts and related disciplines [300054137], humanities [300054136], disciplines (concept) [300054135], Disciplines (hierarchy name) [300054134], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
